<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Lab Final Practice Exam</title>
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif; background: #0f1117; color: #e8eaf0; min-height: 100vh; padding: 1.5rem 1rem 3rem; }
  .container { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  h1 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .subtitle { font-size: 13px; color: #666; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .top-tabs { display: flex; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; background: #1a1d27; border: 1px solid #2a2d3a; border-radius: 12px; padding: 5px; }
  .top-tab { flex: 1; padding: 9px 12px; border-radius: 8px; border: none; background: transparent; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #666; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; font-family: inherit; }
  .top-tab.active { background: #252836; color: #3ecf8e; border: 1px solid #2a3a30; }
  .top-tab:hover:not(.active) { color: #aaa; }
  .top-panel { display: none; }
  .top-panel.active { display: block; }
  .score-bar { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; background: #1a1d27; border: 1px solid #2a2d3a; border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px 18px; margin-bottom: 2rem; position: sticky; top: 0.5rem; z-index: 10; }
  .score-circle { width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 50%; background: conic-gradient(#3ecf8e calc(var(--pct, 0) * 1%), #2a2d3a 0); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; transition: background 0.4s; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .score-inner { width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%; background: #1a1d27; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #3ecf8e; }
  .score-text { font-size: 14px; color: #aaa; }
  .score-text strong { color: #e8eaf0; font-size: 16px; display: block; }
  .section-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #3ecf8e; margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; padding-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #2a2d3a; }
  .q-card { background: #1a1d27; border: 1px solid #2a2d3a; border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
  .q-card.answered-correct { border-color: #3ecf8e44; }
  .q-card.answered-wrong { border-color: #ff6b6b44; }
  .q-num { font-size: 11px; color: #555; margin-bottom: 6px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .q-text { font-size: 15px; color: #d0d4e0; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .q-text span.key { color: #7eb8f7; font-weight: 600; }
  .btn-row { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .opt-btn { padding: 7px 16px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #3a3d4e; background: #252836; font-size: 13px; color: #c8ccd8; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s; font-family: inherit; }
  .opt-btn:hover:not(.disabled) { background: #2e3245; border-color: #4a4d60; color: #fff; }
  .opt-btn.correct { background: #0e3024; border-color: #3ecf8e; color: #3ecf8e; font-weight: 600; }
  .opt-btn.wrong { background: #2d1414; border-color: #ff6b6b; color: #ff6b6b; }
  .opt-btn.disabled { cursor: default; pointer-events: none; }
  .feedback { font-size: 12px; margin-top: 10px; padding: 8px 12px; border-radius: 8px; display: none; line-height: 1.5; }
  .feedback.show { display: block; }
  .feedback.right { background: #0e3024; color: #3ecf8e; }
  .feedback.wrong-f { background: #2d1414; color: #ff9999; }
  .reveal-btn { padding: 7px 16px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #3a3d4e; background: transparent; font-size: 13px; color: #888; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; transition: all 0.15s; }
  .reveal-btn:hover { background: #252836; color: #c8ccd8; border-color: #4a4d60; }
  .answer-box { margin-top: 12px; padding: 14px 16px; border-radius: 10px; background: #13181f; border-left: 3px solid #3ecf8e; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.7; color: #b8bcc8; display: none; }
  .answer-box.show { display: block; }
  .answer-box strong { color: #e0e4f0; font-weight: 600; }
  .answer-box .disease { margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .answer-box .disease:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .cell-stage { display: flex; justify-content: center; margin: 8px 0 14px; }
  .ap-wrap { display: none; margin-top: 12px; }
  .ap-wrap.show { display: block; }
  .ap-wrap svg { width: 100%; max-width: 580px; display: block; margin: 0 auto; }
  .hint { font-size: 11px; color: #555; margin-top: 8px; font-style: italic; }
  .sub-tabs { display: flex; gap: 5px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .sub-tab { padding: 7px 14px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid #2a2d3a; background: transparent; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #666; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; font-family: inherit; }
  .sub-tab.active { background: #1e2d22; border-color: #3ecf8e; color: #3ecf8e; }
  .sub-tab:hover:not(.active) { color: #aaa; border-color: #3a3d4e; }
  .sub-panel { display: none; }
  .sub-panel.active { display: block; }
  .sub-tab2 { padding: 7px 14px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid #2a2d3a; background: transparent; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #666; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; font-family: inherit; }
  .sub-tab2.active { background: #1e2030; border-color: #7eb8f7; color: #7eb8f7; }
  .sub-tab2:hover:not(.active) { color: #aaa; border-color: #3a3d4e; }
  .sub-panel2 { display: none; }
  .sub-panel2.active { display: block; }
  .tip-card { background: #1a1d27; border: 1px solid #2a2d3a; border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .tip-disease { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #3ecf8e; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .tip-hook { font-size: 15px; color: #fff; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 8px 12px; background: #13181f; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #7eb8f7; }
  .tip-body { font-size: 13px; color: #aaa; line-height: 1.7; }
  .tip-body span { color: #e0e4f0; font-weight: 600; }
  .fc-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 16px; }
  .fc-wrap { perspective: 800px; height: 210px; cursor: pointer; }
  .fc-inner { position: relative; width: 100%; height: 100%; transform-style: preserve-3d; transition: transform 0.55s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1); }
  .fc-wrap.flipped .fc-inner { transform: rotateY(180deg); }
  .fc-front, .fc-back { position: absolute; inset: 0; border-radius: 14px; backface-visibility: hidden; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; padding: 1.25rem; text-align: center; }
  .fc-front { background: #1a1d27; border: 1px solid #2a2d3a; }
  .fc-back { background: #13181f; border: 1px solid #3ecf8e44; transform: rotateY(180deg); align-items: flex-start; text-align: left; justify-content: flex-start; padding-top: 1rem; overflow: hidden; }
  .fc-name { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .fc-alias { font-size: 11px; color: #555; }
  .fc-tap { font-size: 11px; color: #444; margin-top: 18px; }
  .fc-row { margin-bottom: 9px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5; }
  .fc-row:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .fc-lbl { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #3ecf8e; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .fc-val { color: #c8ccd8; }
  .match-score-bar { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .match-score-txt { font-size: 13px; color: #888; }
  .match-score-txt strong { color: #3ecf8e; }
  .reset-btn { padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #3a3d4e; background: transparent; font-size: 12px; color: #888; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; transition: all 0.15s; }
  .reset-btn:hover { background: #252836; color: #c8ccd8; }
  .match-cols { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; }
  .match-col-lbl { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #555; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .match-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .match-item { padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid #2a2d3a; background: #1a1d27; font-size: 13px; color: #c8ccd8; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s; line-height: 1.4; min-height: 54px; display: flex; align-items: center; }
  .match-item:hover:not(.matched):not(.wrong-flash) { border-color: #4a4d60; background: #252836; color: #fff; }
  .match-item.selected { border-color: #7eb8f7; background: #0d1e30; color: #7eb8f7; }
  .match-item.matched { border-color: #3ecf8e55; background: #0e3024; color: #3ecf8e; cursor: default; pointer-events: none; }
  .match-item.wrong-flash { border-color: #ff6b6b; background: #2d1414; color: #ff6b6b; }
  .match-complete { text-align: center; padding: 1.5rem; background: #0e3024; border: 1px solid #3ecf8e55; border-radius: 14px; margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 15px; color: #3ecf8e; font-weight: 600; display: none; }
  .match-complete.show { display: block; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <h1>Lab Final — Practice</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">Physiology Lab &nbsp;·&nbsp; Chaffey College</p>

  <div class="top-tabs">
    <button class="top-tab active" onclick="switchTop('exam')">Practice Exam</button>
    <button class="top-tab" onclick="switchTop('gi')">GI Diseases</button>
    <button class="top-tab" onclick="switchTop('labs')">Other Labs</button>
    <button class="top-tab" onclick="switchTop('blood')">Blood Typing</button>
    <button class="top-tab" onclick="switchTop('tools')">Tools &amp; Methods</button>
  </div>

  <!-- PRACTICE EXAM -->
  <div class="top-panel active" id="panel-exam">
    <div class="score-bar">
      <div class="score-circle" id="scoreCircle" style="--pct:0">
        <div class="score-inner" id="scoreInner">0</div>
      </div>
      <div class="score-text">
        <strong id="scoreLabel">0 / 9</strong>
        interactive questions answered
      </div>
      <button class="reset-btn" style="margin-left:auto" onclick="resetExam()">Reset</button>
    </div>

    <div class="section-label">Short answer</div>
    <div class="q-card" id="card-gi">
      <div class="q-num">Question 1</div>
      <div class="q-text">Name any <span class="key">4 gastrointestinal diseases</span> and describe the symptoms, affected area, and treatment for each.</div>
      <button class="reveal-btn" onclick="toggleAnswer('gi', this)">Show answer</button>
      <div class="answer-box" id="gi">
        <div class="disease"><strong>GERD</strong> — Symptoms: heartburn, acid regurgitation, chest pain. Area: esophagus / LES. Treatment: PPIs, antacids, lifestyle changes.</div>
        <div class="disease"><strong>IBS</strong> — Symptoms: cramping, bloating, alternating constipation/diarrhea (no structural damage). Area: large intestine (colon). Treatment: low-FODMAP diet, stress management.</div>
        <div class="disease"><strong>Gallstones</strong> — Symptoms: sharp RUQ pain after fatty food, nausea. Area: gallbladder. Treatment: cholecystectomy.</div>
        <div class="disease"><strong>Gastric Ulcers</strong> — Symptoms: burning stomach pain worse when empty, nausea. Area: stomach lining (mucosa). Treatment: PPIs + antibiotics (H. pylori); avoid NSAIDs.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="q-card" id="card-ecg">
      <div class="q-num">Question 2</div>
      <div class="q-text">How many <span class="key">leads</span> did you use to record your ECG?</div>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <button class="opt-btn" onclick="choose(this,'ecg',true)">3 leads</button>
        <button class="opt-btn" onclick="choose(this,'ecg',false)">6 leads</button>
        <button class="opt-btn" onclick="choose(this,'ecg',false)">10 leads</button>
        <button class="opt-btn" onclick="choose(this,'ecg',false)">12 leads</button>
      </div>
      <div class="feedback" id="ecg-fb">3 electrodes (RA, LA, LL) producing Lead II — the single tracing used for all your interval measurements.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="q-card" id="card-wbc">
      <div class="q-num">Question 3</div>
      <div class="q-text">Give <span class="key">2 reasons</span> why a physician would order a WBC differential count.</div>
      <button class="reveal-btn" onclick="toggleAnswer('wbc', this)">Show answer</button>
      <div class="answer-box" id="wbc">
        <strong>1. Diagnose infection or inflammation</strong> — elevated neutrophils = bacterial; elevated lymphocytes = viral; elevated eosinophils = allergy/parasitic.<br><br>
        <strong>2. Diagnose hematologic disorders</strong> — abnormal morphology or counts can indicate leukemia, lymphoma, anemia, or immunodeficiency.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="q-card" id="card-ap">
      <div class="q-num">Question 4</div>
      <div class="q-text"><span class="key">Draw the action potential</span> and how sodium and potassium permeability changes. Label your axes.</div>
      <button class="reveal-btn" onclick="toggleAP(this)">Show diagram</button>
      <div class="ap-wrap" id="apWrap">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 580 320" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <line x1="70" y1="20" x2="70" y2="265" stroke="#444" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <line x1="70" y1="265" x2="545" y2="265" stroke="#444" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <polygon points="70,15 66,26 74,26" fill="#444"/>
          <polygon points="550,265 538,261 538,269" fill="#444"/>
          <text x="20" y="148" font-size="11" fill="#888" text-anchor="middle" transform="rotate(-90,20,148)" font-family="Segoe UI,sans-serif">Membrane potential (mV)</text>
          <text x="310" y="295" font-size="11" fill="#888" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Segoe UI,sans-serif">Time (ms)</text>
          <line x1="65" y1="210" x2="545" y2="210" stroke="#2a2d3a" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="5,5"/>
          <text x="60" y="214" font-size="10" fill="#666" text-anchor="end" font-family="Segoe UI,sans-serif">-55</text>
          <line x1="65" y1="228" x2="545" y2="228" stroke="#2a2d3a" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="5,5"/>
          <text x="60" y="232" font-size="10" fill="#666" text-anchor="end" font-family="Segoe UI,sans-serif">-70</text>
          <line x1="65" y1="70" x2="545" y2="70" stroke="#2a2d3a" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="5,5"/>
          <text x="60" y="74" font-size="10" fill="#666" text-anchor="end" font-family="Segoe UI,sans-serif">+35</text>
          <text x="60" y="258" font-size="10" fill="#666" text-anchor="end" font-family="Segoe UI,sans-serif">-90</text>
          <polyline points="70,232 145,232 160,224 172,64 188,64 200,115 216,200 240,232 545,232" fill="none" stroke="#e8873a" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="7,4" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <polyline points="70,235 155,235 170,235 185,195 210,115 242,75 275,115 315,225 360,235 545,235" fill="none" stroke="#3ecf8e" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="4,4" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <polyline points="70,228 145,228 158,210 168,68 205,68 245,255 285,228 370,228 545,228" fill="none" stroke="#7eb8f7" stroke-width="3" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <circle cx="158" cy="210" r="4" fill="#7eb8f7"/>
          <text x="163" y="206" font-size="10" fill="#7eb8f7" font-family="Segoe UI,sans-serif">Threshold (-55 mV)</text>
          <circle cx="205" cy="68" r="4" fill="#7eb8f7"/>
          <text x="210" y="65" font-size="10" fill="#7eb8f7" font-family="Segoe UI,sans-serif">Peak (+35 mV)</text>
          <circle cx="245" cy="255" r="4" fill="#7eb8f7"/>
          <text x="210" y="272" font-size="10" fill="#7eb8f7" font-family="Segoe UI,sans-serif">Hyperpolarization (-90 mV)</text>
          <circle cx="285" cy="228" r="4" fill="#7eb8f7"/>
          <text x="290" y="238" font-size="10" fill="#aaa" font-family="Segoe UI,sans-serif">Resting (-70 mV)</text>
          <rect x="370" y="32" width="168" height="70" rx="8" fill="#13181f" stroke="#2a2d3a" stroke-width="1"/>
          <line x1="382" y1="50" x2="408" y2="50" stroke="#7eb8f7" stroke-width="3"/>
          <text x="414" y="54" font-size="11" fill="#d0d4e0" font-family="Segoe UI,sans-serif">Action potential</text>
          <line x1="382" y1="67" x2="408" y2="67" stroke="#e8873a" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="7,4"/>
          <text x="414" y="71" font-size="11" fill="#d0d4e0" font-family="Segoe UI,sans-serif">Na+ permeability</text>
          <line x1="382" y1="84" x2="408" y2="84" stroke="#3ecf8e" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="4,4"/>
          <text x="414" y="88" font-size="11" fill="#d0d4e0" font-family="Segoe UI,sans-serif">K+ permeability</text>
        </svg>
        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#888;margin-top:6px;line-height:1.6;padding:0 4px;">Na+ channels open first = rapid depolarization. Na+ inactivates + K+ opens = repolarization and hyperpolarization overshoot. K+ channels close slowly = return to resting.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-label">True or false</div>
    <div class="q-card" id="card-epi">
      <div class="q-num">True or False</div>
      <div class="q-text">It is <span class="key">abnormal</span> to find epithelial cells in urine.</div>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <button class="opt-btn" onclick="choose(this,'epi',false)">True</button>
        <button class="opt-btn" onclick="choose(this,'epi',true)">False</button>
      </div>
      <div class="feedback" id="epi-fb">False — small numbers of epithelial cells are normal; they shed naturally from the urinary tract lining.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="q-card" id="card-refract">
      <div class="q-num">True or False</div>
      <div class="q-text">A <span class="key">refractometer</span> measures specific gravity.</div>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <button class="opt-btn" onclick="choose(this,'refract',true)">True</button>
        <button class="opt-btn" onclick="choose(this,'refract',false)">False</button>
      </div>
      <div class="feedback" id="refract-fb">True — it measures how light bends through a solution, which correlates directly to specific gravity.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="q-card" id="card-neurosim">
      <div class="q-num">True or False</div>
      <div class="q-text"><span class="key">Neurosim</span> is a computer program.</div>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <button class="opt-btn" onclick="choose(this,'neurosim',true)">True</button>
        <button class="opt-btn" onclick="choose(this,'neurosim',false)">False</button>
      </div>
      <div class="feedback" id="neurosim-fb">True — Neurosim is a simulation software used to model nerve and muscle electrophysiology in lab.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-label">Fill in the blank</div>
    <div class="q-card" id="card-iv">
      <div class="q-num">Blank 1</div>
      <div class="q-text">The <span class="key">independent variable</span> is plotted on the ________ axis.</div>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <button class="opt-btn" onclick="choose(this,'iv',true)">X (horizontal)</button>
        <button class="opt-btn" onclick="choose(this,'iv',false)">Y (vertical)</button>
        <button class="opt-btn" onclick="choose(this,'iv',false)">Z (depth)</button>
      </div>
      <div class="feedback" id="iv-fb">X-axis — the independent variable is what you control or manipulate.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="q-card" id="card-dv">
      <div class="q-num">Blank 2</div>
      <div class="q-text">The <span class="key">dependent variable</span> is plotted on the ________ axis.</div>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <button class="opt-btn" onclick="choose(this,'dv',false)">X (horizontal)</button>
        <button class="opt-btn" onclick="choose(this,'dv',true)">Y (vertical)</button>
        <button class="opt-btn" onclick="choose(this,'dv',false)">Z (depth)</button>
      </div>
      <div class="feedback" id="dv-fb">Y-axis — the dependent variable is what you measure as a result.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-label">Blood typing</div>
    <div class="q-card" id="card-bt">
      <div class="q-num">Blood Typing Table — Judy</div>
      <div class="q-text">Anti-A clumping: <strong style="color:#3ecf8e">Yes</strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp; Anti-B clumping: <strong style="color:#ff6b6b">No</strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp; Anti-Rh clumping: <strong style="color:#3ecf8e">Yes</strong><br><br>What is Judy's blood type?</div>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <button class="opt-btn" onclick="choose(this,'bt',false)">A-</button>
        <button class="opt-btn" onclick="choose(this,'bt',true)">A+</button>
        <button class="opt-btn" onclick="choose(this,'bt',false)">B+</button>
        <button class="opt-btn" onclick="choose(this,'bt',false)">AB+</button>
        <button class="opt-btn" onclick="choose(this,'bt',false)">O+</button>
      </div>
      <div class="feedback" id="bt-fb">A+ — Anti-A clumps = A antigen present. Anti-B doesn't clump = no B antigen. Anti-Rh clumps = Rh positive.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-label">Cell identification — stations 1-4</div>
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:#666;margin-bottom:1rem;">Identify each WBC by nucleus shape, granules, and cytoplasm amount.</p>

    <div class="q-card" id="card-s1">
      <div class="q-num">Station 1</div>
      <div class="cell-stage">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 140 140" width="140" height="140" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <circle cx="70" cy="70" r="62" fill="#2a1818" stroke="#5a3030" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <ellipse cx="52" cy="65" rx="14" ry="16" fill="#7a5aa0" stroke="#9a7ac0" stroke-width="1"/>
          <ellipse cx="70" cy="55" rx="13" ry="15" fill="#7a5aa0" stroke="#9a7ac0" stroke-width="1"/>
          <ellipse cx="88" cy="66" rx="13" ry="15" fill="#7a5aa0" stroke="#9a7ac0" stroke-width="1"/>
          <line x1="64" y1="62" x2="69" y2="58" stroke="#9a7ac0" stroke-width="1.5"/>
