      <div style="background:#13181f;border-radius:10px;padding:12px 14px;margin-bottom:1rem;font-size:13px;color:#aaa;line-height:1.6;border-left:3px solid #7eb8f7;">
        <strong style="color:#e0e4f0">Case:</strong> Barbara, 46, feels abnormally cold, gained 20 lbs, constant fatigue. Lab results: T4 = 2.2 (low), T3 = 33 (low), TSH = 0.2 (low).
